The forces of the mega strike gather
The League's unions and the National Association of Workers' Councils will, Friday, constitute their strike commission, which will be responsible for coordinating the indefinite strike on Monday.
On Saturday, a general protest assembly will be held and on Monday, the day of the final vote on the Health Insurance Act, the strike will begin.
This action will certainly cause important caps in traffic as rail traffic will be stopped almost entirely and BKV employees (common transport company) will also strike until 1 p.m.
