And it's that, choosing the right car insurance, is even harder than choosing the vehicle model.
Car insurance is an agreement between an insurance company and the insurer.
This compromise is based on an insurance contract, which establishes that the company receives the value of the premium granted and in exchange becomes responsible for the obligation to pay compensation in the event of a disaster.
The premium is the price of the insurance, which takes into account various factors, such as age, sex, seniority of the driving licence, marital status, type of vehicle to ensure or use, among others.
Insurance companies establish their prices according to statistics, so that the higher the probability of an accident is, the higher the rate to be paid.
This is why people over 25 years of age and women have to pay lower premiums, since statistics show that these people have lower claims than their caution.
Similarly, using censuses, the companies concluded that married persons tend to have fewer accidents than single drivers.
The use of the vehicle will influence the frequency, and therefore the probability of an accident.
By increasing the frequency the probabilities increase.
There are many variables that insurers take into account when setting the premium price.
For this reason, the driver must carefully study the situation to choose the car insurance that best suits his profile.
We will present here the most significant variables when choosing one or the other type of insurance, so that it, in addition to adapting to the characteristics of the insurer, offers it a reasonable price.
Young people under the age of 25 must face various disadvantages when entering into a contract with an insurance contract at an affordable price, as can be the low experience in driving and driving license seniority.
Although the ideal to be well insured is a risk insurance, other more economic options exist.
The most anticipated drivers can opt for a free risk insurance, so that they obtain the coverage of any risk insurance but at a more affordable price.
