\"The portion of the damage the customer pays will be established according to the value of the premium, which will be higher the amount will be lower,\" explains Luis Noguera, the official in Spain of First Europe, online insurance mediator.
Another option is extended third party insurance, so that the customer provides protection to deal with damage caused to third parties, but for those caused on his own car.
In addition, it would be covered against the theft, fire and loss of the vehicle.
Advice.
If you are a 25-year-old, try to be careful and avoid the disaster as far as possible, as it will affect the bonus, which can reduce the price of insurance in the future.
