For pensioners, insurance at all risks with free will is preferable (i.e. EUR 150), or extended third party insurance when the insurer has a high level of bonus.
It must be said that car insurance is something important, not only because it covers the driver in the face of possible accidents, but also because it represents an important expense, that is why it is fundamental to properly study the insurance that best suits us according to our personal situation.
